author: Flo
content:
I love the image of being under the lights with that red ball of lights in lower right better than your image of the subterranean tunnel. So if these two were mine, I would have chosen the red ball of lights image! But, lol, since I'm not current with popular music, I have no idea what song might go with this image.

The only song I can think of is "Rudolf the Red-Nosed Reindeer"!
